summary: Changing the coin texture into American currency.
descriptionHtml:
Changing the coin texture into American currency.

Place the \"clutter\" folder into your \"Textures\" folder. you know the drill.

Check out British currency - http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=1480

Bug: There is one but i\'v noticed with this texture\' there\'s a slight gold tint to it, I think that\'s coded into the game, though.
author: FoolsPower
